{"type":"message","id":"b61898d0","parentId":"17df6808","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:36:06.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你问得对！让我澄清一下配置层级：\n\n### 正确位置是 **Agent 级配置**，不是全局配置\n\n根据 OpenClaw 的设计：\n- **全局配置** `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` — 控制 Gateway 整体行为（通道、安全策略等）\n- **Agent 配置** `~/.openclaw/agents/main/config.json` — 控制具体 Agent 的行为（包括沙箱和文件访问）\n\n要解除文件访问限制，**必须在 Agent 配置中设置** `sandbox: { mode: \"off\" }`。\n\n这是因为文件访问权限是 **按 Agent 粒度控制的**，而不是全局 Gateway 设置。每个 Agent 可以有不同的沙箱策略。\n\n### 验证配置路径\n你的主 Agent 配置应该在这里：\n```bash\n/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/config.json\n```\n\n需要我帮你检查这个文件是否存在，或者直接修改它吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":34177,"output":208,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34385,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772422555444}}
