{"type":"message","id":"3668dd80","parentId":"bf874345","timestamp":"2026-03-02T03:37:30.108Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"成功了！文件已创建在 `/Users/hope/IdeaProjects/test`。\n\n不过有个重要细节：虽然我们关闭了沙箱（`sandbox: { mode: \"off\" }`），但 OpenClaw 的 **工具层** 仍然默认限制 `write`/`read`/`edit` 工具只能访问 workspace。要让这些工具也能直接操作外部文件，还需要额外配置。\n\n### 完整解决方案：\n在 `/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/main/config.json` 中添加 **`fileAccess: \"full\"`**：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"sandbox\": {\n    \"mode\": \"off\"\n  },\n  \"fileAccess\": \"full\"\n}\n```\n\n这样 `write` 工具就能直接用了。需要我帮你更新这个配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":35078,"output":167,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35245,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772422642407}}
