{"type":"message","id":"d650c9ed","parentId":"da1dde0d","timestamp":"2026-03-02T05:48:59.270Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"技能包已准备就绪！现在我们有两个选择：\n\n### 选项1：稍后重试发布\n等待5-10分钟让 GitHub API 限制重置，然后重新运行发布命令。\n\n### 选项2：手动上传到 ClawHub\n我可以帮你生成一个完整的技能包，你可以手动上传到 ClawHub 网站。\n\n**技能包位置**: `/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/github-contribution/openclaw-github-contribution-1.0.0.tgz`\n\n你希望我：\n1. **等待几分钟后自动重试**？\n2. **或者现在就把技能包给你，你手动上传**？\n\n另外，你的 GitHub 贡献技能内容非常完整，包含了从 fork 到 PR 提交的全流程，这对开源社区会很有帮助！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":58717,"output":170,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58887,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772430530952}}
