{"type":"message","id":"57d577c5","parentId":"95a4a238","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:12:50.337Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"GitHub API 速率限制持续存在。这可能是因为：\n\n1. **你的 GitHub 账户有严格的 API 限制**\n2. **ClawHub 服务端的 GitHub API 使用达到了限制**\n\n### 建议的解决方案：\n\n**选项1：手动上传到 ClawHub 网站**\n- 访问 https://clawhub.com/publish\n- 上传技能包文件：`/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/github-contribution/openclaw-github-contribution-1.0.0.tgz`\n\n**选项2：配置 GitHub Personal Access Token**\n```bash\n# 创建 GitHub PAT 并设置环境变量\nexport GITHUB_TOKEN=your_github_pat_here\n# 然后重试发布\n```\n\n**选项3：稍后再试**\n等待更长时间（比如1小时）让 API 限制完全重置。\n\n你希望选择哪种方式？我可以帮你准备相应的步骤！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":59973,"output":198,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60171,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772431959758}}
