{"type":"message","id":"d2069853","parentId":"60af7458","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:14:35.860Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看来问题不在本地 token，而是 **ClawHub 服务端的 GitHub API 使用达到了速率限制**。\n\n### 最佳解决方案：手动上传\n\n让我为你准备手动上传的完整步骤：\n\n1. **技能包文件位置**：\n   ```\n   /opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/github-contribution/openclaw-github-contribution-1.0.0.tgz\n   ```\n\n2. **手动上传步骤**：\n   - 访问 https://clawhub.com/publish\n   - 登录你的 ClawHub 账户（Linux2010）\n   - 点击 \"Upload Skill Package\"\n   - 选择上面的 `.tgz` 文件\n   - 填写技能信息：\n     - **Name**: GitHub Contribution Workflow\n     - **Slug**: github-contribution  \n     - **Version**: 1.0.0\n     - **Tags**: github, contribution, opensource, pr\n     - **Changelog**: Initial release: Complete GitHub contribution workflow for open source projects including fork, sync, development, and PR submission with Chrome browser support.\n\n这样可以绕过 CLI 的 API 限制，直接通过网站上传。需要我帮你打开浏览器到发布页面吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":60557,"output":258,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60815,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772432064715}}
