{"type":"message","id":"80a0c6d5","parentId":"1a9e73ae","timestamp":"2026-03-02T06:17:00.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"正在通过 Chrome 浏览器打开 ClawHub 网站。请检查你的 Chrome 浏览器是否已打开并加载了 ClawHub 页面。\n\n如果页面没有自动打开，你可以手动访问：\n- **ClawHub 主站**: https://clawhub.ai\n- **或者直接访问**: https://clawhub.com\n\n一旦你看到 ClawHub 网站，请：\n1. **登录你的账户**（Linux2010）\n2. **寻找 \"Publish\" 或 \"Upload Skill\" 按钮**\n3. **上传技能包文件**：`/opt/homebrew/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/github-contribution/openclaw-github-contribution-1.0.0.tgz`\n\n需要我提供更详细的网页操作指导吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":65406,"output":164,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772432198542}}
